Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.13,0:00:13.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come watch, it's time for the appearance{\i0}\N{\i1}of the three leaves! (yay){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.35,0:00:18.85,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Three Leaves, Three Colors"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:22.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Morning! I'll have three bowls{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:25.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Did you eat, eat, eat, eat up your{\i0}\N{\i1}feminine charm along with your food?){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.98,0:00:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, wait, wait a minute! I'm bad at P.E....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.15,0:00:32.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(I heard something good--{\i0}\N{\i1}I've found her weakness... Sorry){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.41,0:00:36.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What I really want is to have fun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.12,0:00:38.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With my f-r-i-e-n-d-s!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:42.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Try talking about silly things{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:47.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like our love lives and other stuff like that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:47.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, why{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:48.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:49.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have any friends?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:50.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"My, you are direct!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:51.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're arrogant{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And high-handed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:52.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...etc.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:00:53.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"You have no reservations, do you?!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:01:00.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are the three leaves running wild?!{\i0}\N{\i1}No one can stop them!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:03.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you eating here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:06.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you don't have friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:07.78,Main,,0,0,0,,My, you are direct!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.78,0:01:12.32,Main,,0,0,0,,She cried at the end for some reason, though.\NI wonder if something was wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.32,0:01:13.20,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:13.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Ready, set!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:15.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go, I, my, ambiguous me! (Go!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:16.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mind's asleep... (zzz...){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:20.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel refreshed! Oh, really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:23.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the three of us (fever!){\i0}\N{\i1}we have transcendent wisdom?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:26.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But when we're actually together, it's just noisy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:26.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(One more time!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:28.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look! Going my way forcefully forward! (Go! Go!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:30.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forward! Yeah, going my way up! (Jump! Jump!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:33.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Full speed ahead!{\i0}\N{\i1}Thanks for your hard work{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:36.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the story of my (wow!){\i0}\N{\i1}kind of strange and unusual{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.97,0:01:40.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Best and strongest life in history{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:43.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leave her alone or Satan will burst out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:45.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure this is a high school girl's{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:46.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Normal?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:46.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyday?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:48.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}School life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:55.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:56.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.16,0:02:04.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Really, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:36.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:39.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Not at all. It's my job as class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:45.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:47.71,Main,,0,0,0,,C'mon, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:58.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:01.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.14,0:03:03.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry! I'm so hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:07.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to wait until\NI get back to the classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Shortcut time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:12.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll wipe off my indoor shoes after!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:36.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:45.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Are those--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:49.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-These are... bread crusts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:52.31,Main,,0,0,0,,"These Are Bread Crusts"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:57.11,Main,,0,0,0,,You still eat as much as ever, Futaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:04:00.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is me holding back, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:02.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:07.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Actually, I wonder how you eat\Nso little, Hayama. Is that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:10.38,Main,,0,0,0,,My body is more efficient than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:12.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Want to eat some of my side dishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:14.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Can I?! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:15.92,Main,,0,0,0,,You can have some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:19.18,Main,,0,0,0,,What is the matter with the two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:24.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you eating here, too? How bothersome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:26.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:31.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You just said "bothersome"!\NWow, a real rich girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:35.98,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, now. Time to "hold back."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:38.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Really, now. What is the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:43.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, we haven't introduced ourselves yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:47.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Hayama. I'm doing Class 3 the favor\Nof being their class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:50.00,Main,,0,0,0,,"Doing them the favor"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:53.04,Main,,0,0,0,,This is Futaba Odagiri from the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:54.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet'cha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:05:00.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I am Yoko Nishikawa from Class 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:01.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:03.39,Main,,0,0,0,,You're famous, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:05.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Famous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:11.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine, telling a student not to touch me\Nwith their filthy hands was not proper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:13.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:18.57,Main,,0,0,0,,And I am not secretively eating alone\Nbecause nobody will eat with me after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:20.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Er, we weren't asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:23.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you don't have friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:25.53,Main,,0,0,0,,My, you are direct!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:31.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I do not have similar interests, and I do not\Nknow what to talk about in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:35.83,Main,,0,0,0,,We're talking just fine right now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:59.44,Main,,0,0,0,,This is nice, huh. It's pretty\Nfun to eat outdoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:02.36,Main,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:03.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, the first bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:05.57,Main,,0,0,0,,--Huh?\N--Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:10.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:12.58,Main,,0,0,0,,See you, Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:13.96,Main,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:15.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:21.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, bread crusts are yummy when you\Ndeep fry them and sprinkle sugar on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:24.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Fry them and use sugar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:26.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I have never heard of that.\NWhat kind of recipe is--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:27.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:30.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Our teacher is strict about being on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:39.19,Main,,0,0,0,,We have English next, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:42.53,Main,,0,0,0,,--Yup.\N--Did you do your homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:46.41,Main,,0,0,0,,What odd girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:47.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:59.21,Main,,0,0,0,,...that may have been my first lunch\Nwith others since I came to this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:04.17,Main,,0,0,0,,So this is their class?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I sorta got sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:29.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I so hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:35.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishikawa...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:39.88,Main,,0,0,0,,What's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:53.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I made it to the flash sale on time again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:08:03.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, bread crusts are yummy when you\Ndeep fry them and sprinkle sugar on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:11.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm, do I have any sugar left?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:18.67,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, lunchtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:23.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You're getting a little full of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:25.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Whatever do you mean, Nishiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:29.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I know you badmouthed Kondo\Nto the teacher yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:33.35,Main,,0,0,0,,All I did was deliver the printouts to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:37.27,Main,,0,0,0,,For Kondo, the one on duty, since she\Ndidn't do her job for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:38.85,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:47.24,Main,,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, I want to settle things with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:48.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:50.20,Main,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:51.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be too hard on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:54.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't take orders from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:57.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, I was talking to Hayama, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:04.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they'll think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:16.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:33.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I-It's not as if I was expecting them!\NAnd now I can eat lunch alone, like usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:41.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:48.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, that sucked!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:51.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Futaba...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:53.51,Main,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to take a shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:56.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't want to keep Yoko waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:01.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Yoko. Did you wait long?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:05.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-You're late! Five whole minutes late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:08.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, a nuisance picked a fight with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:11.03,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:11.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:16.20,Main,,0,0,0,,She cried at the end for some reason, though.\NI wonder if something was wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:17.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:19.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Best not to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:27.88,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:31.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it a perv? Like a stalker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:37.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Yamaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:38.47,Main,,0,0,0,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:41.18,Main,,0,0,0,,He's a former family servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:44.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I sincerely apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:46.40,Main,,0,0,0,,What-- Yamaji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:51.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I was laboring under a misapprehension.\NI thought that was just a whim yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:54.15,Main,,0,0,0,,So he was here yesterday, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:57.37,Main,,0,0,0,,But I would accept a whim!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:11:00.74,Main,,0,0,0,,After all, it's a miracle for\NMiss Yoko to make school friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:03.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:07.00,Main,,0,0,0,,For you, a ruined shadow of the\Nrich young lady you once were,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:10.50,Main,,0,0,0,,yet unable to let go of your upper-class\Nattitude after the company's bankruptcy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:13.47,Main,,0,0,0,,due to your pampered upbringing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:19.10,Main,,0,0,0,,to make friends with normal commoners\Nat school must surely be a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:20.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:23.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not how it is! Yamaji's exaggerating!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:29.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Please take care of Miss Yoko forever!\NAs her school friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, shall we eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:45.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:46.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.96,0:11:50.21,Main,,0,0,0,,E-Er, listen, my--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:56.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't it nice to be outside? It's so much\Nfun to eat surrounded by nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:57.09,Main,,0,0,0,,My--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:12:00.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I {\i1}knew {\i0}you couldn't really make friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:03.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Yamaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:20.16,Main,,0,0,0,,How horribly noisy they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.16,0:12:24.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd at least like to quietly enjoy\Na book during break time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:29.29,Main,,0,0,0,,These loud voices aren't ladylike at all.\NHow can I be social with such people?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:33.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yoko! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.59,0:12:36.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Futaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:40.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Her smile is so bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:42.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:47.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, I forgot my math textbook.\NCan I borrow yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:51.27,Main,,0,0,0,,My class doesn't have math today,\Nso I didn't bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:55.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, really? Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:57.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:13:01.49,Main,,0,0,0,,In the old days, I would have\Nhad a servant fetch it at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:04.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it's not {\i1}that {\i0}big a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:16.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Phew, I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:18.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:23.26,Main,,0,0,0,,About the textbook? No worries,\Nit's my bad for forgetting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:27.93,Main,,0,0,0,,And she hardly pays attention\Nin class anyway, book or no book.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:29.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:35.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, Hayama, you say the\Nrudest things with no hesitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:37.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? Didn't I speak the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:41.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, lunchtime! Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:46.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:49.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? You don't know what white bread is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:52.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, but why are you eating a whole loaf?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.75,0:13:55.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Buying more than one thing is too much work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:57.96,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:00.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you having bread crusts again, Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:05.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes! Look how many you can get\Nfor such little money!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:08.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I was so moved the first time I saw these!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:11.73,Main,,0,0,0,,But don't you need more nutrients?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:14.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Not to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:22.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Now they're perfectly nutritious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:30.70,Main,,0,0,0,,My poor Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:31.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:32.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Yamaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:36.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll have to call the police\Nif you keep trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:38.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm authorized to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:41.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I refill the school vending machines.\NIt's a side job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:43.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I see! That's fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:46.26,Main,,0,0,0,,No, stalkers are not fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:47.72,Main,,0,0,0,,That is unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,What about my quietly watching\Nher unseen from the shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:52.35,Main,,0,0,0,,makes you think I'm a stalker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:57.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm just concerned for Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:15:01.28,Main,,0,0,0,,No sooner had I taken over my late\Ngrandfather's position as servant
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:03.28,Main,,0,0,0,,than I was suddenly let go...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:07.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so worried about how the young miss\Nwill get along among the common folk,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:10.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to keep an eye on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:13.91,Main,,0,0,0,,She has such an explosive temper,\Nand when she doesn't get her way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:16.17,Main,,0,0,0,,it triggers a chemical reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:18.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Yamaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:20.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko, take these!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.09,0:15:24.51,Main,,0,0,0,,They're clearance goods from my job,\Nbut they're not {\i1}quite {\i0}expired yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:26.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yamaji, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:30.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, my next job is waiting. Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:38.31,Main,,0,0,0,,If he pities you that much,\Nhe should give you cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:41.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet he's barely making ends meet, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:42.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I can't believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:43.15,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flan"\NHonestly, I can't believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:45.95,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flan"\NDoes he think {\i1}these {\i0}will make me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:48.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Make me feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:50.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:54.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Drat! Now I've been mortified, thanks to Yamaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:59.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I've finally made friends--I have to\Nmake sure not to turn them off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:06.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko, here is today's\Nexpired food. Please, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:11.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Why does he have to do this during lunchtime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:15.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:17.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll take my leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:24.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Keep a cool head, Yoko. Don't jump for joy\Nand make them think you have no decorum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:27.74,Main,,0,0,0,,How wonderful! It's cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:30.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Good for you, Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:33.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, cheese is healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:38.79,Main,,0,0,0,,So, you two, what are your favorite foods?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:39.79,Main,,0,0,0,,White rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:41.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Not bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:46.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Bread kinda feels like a snack.\NI like rice better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:48.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Then why not pack your own lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:50.59,Main,,0,0,0,,No time in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:52.43,Main,,0,0,0,,What's your fave, Hayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:53.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:58.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Why, it's mille-feuille!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:05.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I like salted fish paste,\Nis there a problem with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:06.40,Main,,0,0,0,,No problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:10.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, that stuff is good!\NGoes nicely with rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:13.78,Main,,0,0,0,,What's yours, Yoko? Cheese?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:18.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to give an answer\Nthey won't think is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:21.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Something commoners would accept...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:24.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Right now, I like flan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:27.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Geh, flan?! But that'd be {\i1}gross {\i0}with rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:28.76,Main,,0,0,0,,With rice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:33.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Are normal people's favorite foods\Nthings that pair well with rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:35.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to answer right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:38.68,Main,,0,0,0,,H-How about pink codfish flakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:40.18,Main,,0,0,0,,You like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:43.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayonnaise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:45.65,Main,,0,0,0,,At least that's the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:50.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you used to be rich?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:56.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What now? At this rate,\Nthey might start to hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:07.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:18.26,Main,,0,0,0,,They were so happy about\Nthe fried bread crusts, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:35.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama! Futaba! Today...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:38.28,Main,,0,0,0,,...I made rice balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:41.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought she and bread crusts were exclusive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:44.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I can cook if I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:47.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow. I can't make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:52.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind sharing, if you'd like some.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:54.51,Main,,0,0,0,,She can't mean balls of {\i1}just {\i0}rice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:56.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:00.35,Main,,0,0,0,,It really is just rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:04.02,Main,,0,0,0,,You said you liked rice, Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:06.27,Main,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:08.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Rice balls are surprisingly complex, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:11.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Lots of different possible fillings...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:16.91,Main,,0,0,0,,These have no fillings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.20,Main,,0,0,0,,None?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:22.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to use salted fish paste,\Nsince Hayama likes it, but it was expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:24.16,Main,,0,0,0,,For my sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:26.50,Main,,0,0,0,,But in rice balls...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:30.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Getting the salt level in the\Nrice right is tricky, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:34.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I forgot to add the salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,D-Did I fail again? I thought they'd be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:46.02,Main,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:56.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:01.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:05.08,Main,,0,0,0,,L-Listen, please don't force yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:08.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Rice is tasty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:13.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama... Futaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:24.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Go on, Yoko, you gotta eat too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:26.81,Main,,0,0,0,,You can have one of my Vienna sausages.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:28.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:30.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm having thirds!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:31.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Futaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:34.69,Main,,0,0,0,,"Central Shopping Arcade"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:38.03,Main,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't do anything\Nfor me in return, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:42.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Since we're... friends... and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:45.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be shy, Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:48.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, since we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:53.21,Main,,0,0,0,,They were free tickets anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:58.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I have a family member who wins\Nthis stuff a lot. Oh, here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:20:59.76,Main,,0,0,0,,A bathhouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:01.09,Main,,0,0,0,,"Healing Waters"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:13.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing better than a bath for us Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:17.28,Main,,0,0,0,,You said it. And this one smells nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:23.99,Main,,0,0,0,,This is great. It's been so long since\NI could stretch my legs out in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:27.37,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:30.58,Main,,0,0,0,,...to heat enough water for a bath this big...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:33.92,Main,,0,0,0,,How much must the utility bills be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:35.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Just have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:36.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I lost it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:38.63,Main,,0,0,0,,"Healing Waters"\NSorry, I lost it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:41.38,Main,,0,0,0,,"Healing Waters"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.01,0:21:45.26,Main,,0,0,0,,To think they were even\Nwilling to bathe with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:49.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I was so worried, but I think\NMiss Yoko will survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.10,0:21:51.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.19,0:21:54.69,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I can't waste Hayama's kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:57.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop worrying and have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:22:01.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Another hour... no, at least half a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.49,0:22:03.07,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll get dizzy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:07.33,Main,,0,0,0,,You're gonna boil into Yoko soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.33,0:22:10.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I can keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.62,0:22:14.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.59,0:22:22.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello, my name is Shino Sonobe.\NI'm the Nishikawa family's former maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:25.43,Main,,0,0,0,,The black-hearted class representative,\Nthe poor girl on a daily bread-crust diet,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.43,0:22:27.01,Main,,0,0,0,,and the walking black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.01,0:22:30.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Their "to each her own color" life is\Nso entertaini-- I mean, wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.35,0:22:35.65,Main,,0,0,0,,And now, listen to the "Rock Scissors Parade."\NRock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:39.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I'm pitch black inside{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.36,0:22:42.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I can't live in luxury{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.99,0:22:46.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if there's lots{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:49.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With three of us, we can eat it all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.58,0:22:52.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Clever and smart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.91,0:22:56.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm living resolutely{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:22:59.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With a full tummy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.63,0:23:02.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how I spend my days{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.63,0:23:05.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What makes me smile?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.72,0:23:06.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Food!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.59,0:23:07.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Money..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.43,0:23:09.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I can't say here"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.10,0:23:12.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We each have our own happiness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:14.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's enjoy life as much as we want{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.98,0:23:16.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's crazy and messy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.10,0:23:19.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look, it's the rock scissors parade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.44,0:23:22.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the three of us gather{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.86,0:23:24.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For rock, paper, scissors{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:26.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll tie{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.45,0:23:29.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it'll never end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:36.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The parade's started, and you have to join{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:39.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The answer to one times three{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:44.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you want to know, then come here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.10,0:23:51.72,Main,,0,0,0,,And so my tumultuous school life began.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.72,0:23:56.48,Main,,0,0,0,,This new dog eat dog world is full of trials,\Nsuch as understanding how to spend break time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.48,0:23:58.61,Main,,0,0,0,,But from now on, I won't lunch alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.61,0:23:59.36,Main,,0,0,0,,"Zwaahhh"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.36,0:24:01.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Shall we eat indoors when it rains?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.65,0:24:02.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.19,0:24:08.57,Main,,0,0,0,,"Next Time: Nothing Good for You Is Tasty"
